1. *Claire* se lako brinula o svojoj deci. (Claire easily took care of her children.)
2. Ona se često *claire* sa svojim prijateljima. (She often *claired* with her friends.)
3. On je bio *Claire* da to uradi. (He was *claired* to do that.)
4. Ona je bila *claire* da to uradi. (She was *claired* to do that.)
5. Ona se *claire* da će biti uspešna. (She *claired* that she will be successful.)